{"parentUuid":"70ec1aab-b457-4c89-973d-22eb7b99209d","isSidechain":false,"promptId":"b54a33ee-797d-4281-a71b-00d971ef26f8","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":"Read /var/www/velocms/RESUME.md and then implement \nthe following:\n\nTRANSLATION SYSTEM — Complete rebuild using \nproven two-layer architecture:\n\nLAYER 1 — UI Strings (static interface text):\n- Remove the existing translation DB table and \n  t() function completely\n- Replace with simple PHP array files:\n  /var/www/velocms/lang/de.php (default)\n  /var/www/velocms/lang/en.php\n- Each file returns an array: \n  ['nav.home' => 'Startseite'] etc.\n- New t('key') function: reads the correct lang \n  file based on vcms_lang cookie, falls back to \n  DE if key not found in EN\n- Language toggle: sets cookie + location.reload()\n- All existing t() keys migrate to these files\n- Admin UI: Admin → Translations shows two columns \n  (DE | EN) as simple editable text fields, \n  auto-saves on blur, EN field triggers DeepL/\n  Anthropic API translation automatically when \n  left empty\n\nLAYER 2 — Content translations (pages, blog, \nbooking):\n- Add _en columns to content tables:\n  pages: title_en, content_en\n  posts: title_en, excerpt_en, content_en  \n  booking_resources: name_en, description_en\n- When DE content is saved, automatically trigger \n  translation via DeepL API (primary) or \n  Anthropic API (fallback) and save to _en column\n- Frontend reads correct column based on \n  vcms_lang cookie\n- Manual EN override: if admin edits _en field \n  directly, set manual_override flag, never \n  auto-overwrite\n\nPROVIDER SETTINGS:\n- Fix: only one provider active at a time \n  (DeepL OR Anthropic, not both)\n- DeepL is primary (cheaper, faster for \n  pure translation)\n- Anthropic is fallback\n\nCLEANUP (run as part of this task):\n- Remove ALL old translation system code: \n  old DB migrations, old t() function, old \n  translation controller, old translation views, \n  old AJAX endpoints\n- Remove translations DB table\n- Verify no traces remain\n\nAFTER IMPLEMENTATION:\n1. Run full PHPUnit test suite\n2. Full codebase audit:\n   - PHP syntax check all files\n   - No hardcoded strings outside lang files\n   - No traces of old translation system\n   - No temp files\n3. Update VELOCMS_MASTERPLAN.md — mark \n   translation system architecture decision\n4. Update RESUME.md and SESSION_LOG.md\n5. Push to GitHub\n6. Tell me what to verify"},"uuid":"f597f45b-3380-4585-b45d-7cf75fbcdced","timestamp":"2026-05-20T09:34:16.035Z","permissionMode":"acceptEdits","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"C:\\Users\\Sascha Zielke","sessionId":"e94faa80-c9ec-40db-a0a9-1fb41aeceb59","version":"2.1.139","gitBranch":"master"}
